        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">PLoS Biology , Tautz et al.</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">2004</TIMEX>) have quantified the <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">bees</ENAMEX>' subjective
