        <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1996</TIMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Heran</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Lindauer</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1963</TIMEX>) likewise observed that <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">honeybees</ENAMEX> flying over lakes
